NAME
  bang - Bash4 Framework for easy script creation

SYNOPSIS
  bang new [path/to/project_name|project_name]

DESCRIPTION
  Creates the bare structure for a new bang project in the
  given path or in the current directory if only the name is given.

  It crates a structure like this:

  my_project*  Your project's executable
  modules/     where script modules will be placed
  tasks/       where bang tasks will be placed
  tests/       where your unit tests will be placed

EXAMPLES
  bang new my_project
  bang new /opt/my_project

SEE ALSO
  bang(1) bang-test(1) bang-run(1)

AUTHOR
  Gustavo Dutra <gustavotkg@gmail.com>
